childRecords.description:
WHEN I log in to POTW
AND my school has 0 Active Payment Request and at least 1 of these payment requests:
- Future
- Expired
- Cancelled
THEN i will be on the Future/Expired/Cancelled payment request landing page
AND I will see the options for the other payment request types
AND I will not see the menu for Active Payment requests
AND the payment request is not shown in School Gateway
